headline: Trane Technologies (NYSE:TT) Misses Q3 Revenue Estimates
summary: HVAC company Trane (NYSE:TT) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, but sales rose 5.5% year on year to $5.74 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.88 per share was 2.7% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Trane Technologies Reports Strong Third Quarter Results
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, October 30, 2025--Trane Technologies plc (NYSE:TT), a global climate innovator, today reported diluted earnings per share (EPS) from continuing operations of $3.82 for the third quarter of 2025. Adjusted continuing EPS was $3.88, up 15 percent.

headline: Trane Technologies: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: DUBLIN (AP) — Trane Technologies plc (TT) on Thursday reported third-quarter profit of $847.6 million. The Dublin-based company said it had profit of $3.78 per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, came to $3.88 per share.
